    <section class="banner">
      <div class="banner-content"> 
        <h1>
          Magic Kingdom Park
        </h1>
        <p>Magic Kingdom Park, nestled in the enchanting town of Bay Lake, Florida, is a world-renowned destination that brings the magic of imagination to life. Opened on October 1, 1971, this iconic park is a haven for dreamers and adventurers alike. Designed and built with meticulous care, it offers visitors a chance to step into a world of wonder and enchantment.</p>
    
        <a href=""> <h4>Learn More</h4></a>
      </div>
  
    </section>

    <section class="main">
      <div>
        <h2>– Operating Hours</h2>
        <p>Experience the magic all year round! The park is open daily from <span>April to October</span>, welcoming visitors from <span>9am to 7pm.</span>  Make sure to plan your visit and immerse yourself in a day filled with unforgettable adventures.</p>
    
        <a href=""><h4>Learn More</h4></a>
