            <p>Our Bahria Town Eye features unique round that take riders to a height of 35 meters where they experience a panoramic view of Bahria Town Karachi.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="/images/vr.jpg" alt="Shark Attack">
          <div class="card-content">
            <h2>SHARK ATTACK</h2>
            <p>Shark Attack can not only rotate around the center, but also can fly up and down. Shark Attack is equipped with wonderful sound effects and attractive LED lights, making it a better way to enjoy the thrill.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="/images/elephant.jpg" alt="Adventure Bay">
          <div class="card-content">
            <h2>ADVENTURE BAY</h2>
            <p>Adventure Bay is a virtual splash factory for the entire family. Minimum 7 water slides and other water features such as tipping cones, hose jets, water guns and loads of other fun-filled features! Hours of fun for kids of all ages!</p>
          </div>
